{"ja314:0.1":"Jataka ","ja314:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja314:0.3":"Pucimandavagga ","ja314:0.4":"4. Lohakumbhijataka ","ja314:1.1":"“Dujjivitamajivimha, ","ja314:1.2":"ye sante na dadamhase; ","ja314:1.3":"Vijjamanesu bhogesu, ","ja314:1.4":"dipam nakamha attano”. ","ja314:2.1":"“Satthi vassasahassani, ","ja314:2.2":"paripunnani sabbaso; ","ja314:2.3":"Niraye paccamananam, ","ja314:2.4":"kada anto bhavissati”. ","ja314:3.1":"“Natthi anto kuto anto, ","ja314:3.2":"na anto patidissati; ","ja314:3.3":"Tada hi pakatam papam, ","ja314:3.4":"mama tuyhanca marisa”. ","ja314:4.1":"“Soham nuna ito gantva, ","ja314:4.2":"yonim laddhana manusim; ","ja314:4.3":"Vadannu silasampanno, ","ja314:4.4":"kahami kusalam bahun”ti. ","ja314:5.1":"Lohakumbhijatakam catuttham. "}